{"tid":1583433,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歐霸踢足全場　武球王成歷史創造者","createTime":"2019-09-20T14:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T05:04:25.000Z","uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3bbf36830fcfee4356eb57ffdb2e097bd6ae7aba","tid":1583433,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20190920/photo/bkn-20190920072725486-0920_00882_001_01b.jpg?20190920072818\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20190920%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190920072725486-0920_00882_001_01b.jpg%3F20190920072818&h=cedb43e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今屆歐霸盃除咗阿仙奴同曼聯廣受關注，中國球迷最緊張就係愛斯賓奴嘅「中國球王」武磊，分組賽開賽，武磊在愛斯賓奴正選上陣主場迎戰費倫斯華路士，並踢足全場，結果踢成1比1，武磊亦見證多項紀錄誕生。<br />\n首先係武磊自己，佢成為2010至11年史浩克04參加歐聯嘅蒿俊閔之後，8年來首位征戰歐洲賽正賽嘅中國球員，如果淨計歐霸盃，更要數到11年前、2008至09年奧地利維也納嘅孫祥。<br />\n今仗踢成1比1，亦令愛斯賓奴創下22場歐洲賽不敗、打破阿積士21場不敗紀錄，此紀錄不計算互射12碼，阿積士嘅紀錄於1994至96年期間所創，而愛斯賓奴並非歐戰常客，其不敗紀錄係橫跨13年。<br />\n紀錄由2006至07年歐戰開始，愛斯賓奴就該屆賽事15場不敗，最終在淘汰賽階段互射12碼落敗，然之後嚟到今屆歐霸盃，球隊於歐霸外圍賽6場不敗，加埋今場，創造連續22場不敗紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n聽講早兩個星期輸比格狗之後比人話要打入冷宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ccb6bca6225a60dc352c1f7f334f03a1740338c","tid":1583433,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:00:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"42794cfda46e226e85778c64037d4c23b601a7f6","tid":1583433,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:03:47.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊 - 會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人 - 食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG151e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=f9034b42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"89382edf35b437f8a3c54381a5581a6ddad65431","tid":1583433,"uid":14075,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:27:45.000Z","msg":"而愛斯賓奴並非歐戰常客，其不敗紀錄係橫跨13年。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無踢就唔洗輸"},{"pid":"b1ab133db65f8de191a299644e4942dd342916bf","tid":1583433,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:31:17.000Z","msg":"中国球員打唔到歐賽都叫紀錄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6cb079d2c30a80c3c3142beef83247e4110531","tid":1583433,"uid":61660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:32:52.000Z","msg":"阿武球王有樣野好過癮係同佢爭位個D唔知點解成日會自己傷"},{"pid":"3f0ca9cd1a3d7be1207d8c9a5f3307c39a235248","tid":1583433,"uid":79403,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:33:18.000Z","msg":"1比1點打破人哋不敗紀錄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f272a07fddb3f287b50dfae3c5933f532e1b6f7","tid":1583433,"uid":80456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:43:21.000Z","msg":"愛斯賓奴創下22場歐洲賽不敗、打破阿積士21場不敗紀錄<br />\n<br />\n咁撚勁，就唔會主場和垃圾隊"},{"pid":"1eda34ec996b51e87587abbc2f03397cbe5b6ee8","tid":1583433,"uid":119094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:43:40.000Z","msg":"佢都算唔錯嘅<br />\n係有班煩鳩盲fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif